timeline.message:
Create a new endpoint to support batch delete;

Ensure the batch update only creates a new filter when uuid is empty;

Don't send requests to Server if no setting changes are found;

Only save changed settings

Make the list of MIME types scrollable;

Put texts in languagestrings;

Add JSDoc;

Use QueryParam for the batch delete endpoint;

For batch operations, the response code is 207 and response body includes
a status code and a message for each operation

